{"tid":866284,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"最近天氣咁好有無人去露營呀","createTime":"2018-10-17T17:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T00:07:53.000Z","uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6c23608a1dfc4e3e052e0326300328912ba060b1","tid":866284,"uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"小弟最近淘左set營同營具諗住十月尾十一月頭就去露<br />\n有無巴打分享下用緊咩營具 特別係煮食用具（同埋食D咩)<br />\n上年去過灣仔今次諗緊會唔會轉地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355bb4605ec5edd015549221ffcf8d7cee276cb6","tid":866284,"uid":12877,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:41:32.000Z","msg":"計劃兩日一夜<br />\n下晝去到營地<br />\n第一餐食韓燒 自備gas爐<br />\n宵夜可能食湯圓<br />\n早餐煎塊漢堡扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宵夜有咩推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1763cbc40454302e84d2ab129323361f52bb24","tid":866284,"uid":278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"路營必須酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竟然冇酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7298b306df1f412b8f61e28b7177ea42ed655b7","tid":866284,"uid":278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e1763cbc40454302e84d2ab129323361f52bb24","tid":866284,"uid":278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"路營必須酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竟然冇酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:46:32.000Z","msg":"露營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0884193a4cb4554073a8bdb3648384f46b9f491d","tid":866284,"uid":33410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"牛排係必備<img